structure.unit: A CABINET FOR HEALTH AND FAMILY SERVICES

law.text:
As used in KRS 194A.600 to 194A.609:
"Council" means the Alzheimer's Disease and Related Disorders Advisory Council;
"Dementia" means Alzheimer's disease and related dementia illnesses and disorders; and
"Office" means the Office on Alzheimer's Disease and Related Disorders.
law.history: Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 6, sec. 3, effective July 14, 2000.
